data.description: Expect to be impressed by this Beautiful upgraded and remodeled home in The Fairways Gated community. Large living space in the main area which is great for entertaining. Formal living room/Office and formal dining room as you enter home. Prepare to be impressed by the beautiful porcelain wood tile throughout the entire home, brand new spacious kitchen with a big island, double ovens, wine cooler,  wall mount pot filler faucet, exotic granite countertop and new cabinets, Family Room with wood burning fireplace, French doors open to the screened private pool area, New fenced yard, new roof, new A/C condenser, new hot water heater, new plumbing, new light fixtures and ceiling fans, new light switches and outlets throughout and so much more. This home is conveniently located only minutes from great shopping and  restaurants, only minutes to the airport, major highways, minutes to all parks and international drive
